channel.title: [PI] Good commands?
channel.description: I can't find very many good snippets for awesome commands. I need stuff that would be good for donors. Such as the ::qspk command. I'd like primarily stuff that does unique anims and gfxs and benifits donors in many small ways. That way I can start giving benifits instead of riches for donations, that way my economy is even better. Or if you know of any good anims/gfx that aren't used by default that I could put into a command, I'd like to know of that too. Yes I have a gfx list, but I want peoples opinions as well. Thank you. :)
